{"tid":1578931,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"大鄉里出城.....去左台灣旅行同睇結他","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T19:32:30.000Z","uid":37078,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11301e53f10a364e585955817cb4289eb3bed985","tid":1578931,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5ewwnvMVvjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5ewwnvMVvjU&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=8f20d255\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5ewwnvMVvjU</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb282d2abcab44fcb10867f4c7dd08345f99721","tid":1578931,"uid":225247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"等左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d96fb01b991148422e1838754d12160f8320675","tid":1578931,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb282d2abcab44fcb10867f4c7dd08345f99721","tid":1578931,"uid":225247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"等左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝...."},{"pid":"d80c935c9c39830dd71699c04d529575c3262bc9","tid":1578931,"uid":13466,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLnkFpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLnkFpy.jpg&h=62e7e5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQsT0py.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQsT0py.jpg&h=e868c1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pG2kFpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpG2kFpz.jpg&h=aa5f10e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QA2464A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQA2464A.jpg&h=1c07e7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyg19hW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhyg19hW.jpg&h=4ecb3261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我8月中都去咗金螞蟻呀！<br />\n入面D結他多到，同老婆去，我都掛住攪D二奶而冷落老婆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，入面嘅見聞都值得一講：<br />\n<br />\n1. 台灣樂器店嘅入貨質素及種類，真係比香港好好多。同事頭婆吹水，佢問：「你們香港Tom lee 的吉他不是都很齊全嗎？」我只有回答一句：「徒有虛名。」<br />\n<br />\n2. 台灣樂器店服務態度真係好到無人有！我入到金螞蟻，基於尊重，我先向事頭婆表明來意：「我乃觀光客，到來是為參觀，請問能否拍照和試結他？」事頭婆明知我係嚟混吉，非但無拒絕，結他仲任我玩任我試、更會行開由我自己玩（我拎上手支支貴野）。<br />\n比著係Tom Lee？貴野例牌鎖頸唔比你隨意拎上手試，就算比你拎到上手，試五分鐘班sales 即刻變身實Q企喺你後面眼超超。<br />\n<br />\n3. 到臨近離開時，事頭婆知我來自香港，就話：「我在新聞有看到香港的情況。你們香港人要加油哦！支持你們！」聽罷，百般滋味在心頭。<br />\n<br />\n結語：無論係貨物質素、種類多樣、服務態度、至乎人性，台灣樂器店都令我難忘。日後有機會搵到錢，有能力買支精品嘅話，必來台灣！"},{"pid":"69a121b90313d1dd274f121a40ee0115a9e39a6b","tid":1578931,"uid":37078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"係同一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老闆同職員都好nice呀"},{"pid":"868ce1b29b94c1ff5304039187d5d390bec03ad1","tid":1578931,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d96fb01b991148422e1838754d12160f8320675","tid":1578931,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb282d2abcab44fcb10867f4c7dd08345f99721","tid":1578931,"uid":225247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"等左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:30:44.000Z","msg":"做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啊 <br />\n<br />\n出新片 大佬好嘢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c19d0ab4150e975f8b381394290a9510be6996","tid":1578931,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3g2aVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3g2aVy.png&h=5ce24a5c&s={SIZE}\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"63c19d0ab4150e975f8b381394290a9510be6996","tid":1578931,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3g2aVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3g2aVy.png&h=5ce24a5c&s={SIZE}\" />"}}